That it's real.

2506
01:42:19,040 --> 01:42:20,860
That it has no imaginary part.

2507
01:42:22,720 --> 01:42:27,680
Now, for a matrix, that's not what it says.

2508
01:42:27,780 --> 01:42:29,840
It doesn't say that the entries are real,

2509
01:42:30,480 --> 01:42:32,440
but it's a kind of reality property.

